# Approach

1. Write manual steps for every action
2. Take input from user
3. Create a parameterized function for the action
   a) Add step by step logic : Precondition before starting logic execution such length, min value req
   b) Use constants as placeholders = 0 / 1 / empty string , add data to it
   c) for each / for loop
   d) Return a value
4. Call the function, get the value, print the value
5. Call the function , get the value as boolean : true / false, print with if ( true value )..else ( false value ) 
